dct_title_s: New Brunswick and Highland Park, New Jersey 1933
dct_description_sm: Map of New Brunswick and Highland Park, N.J. and portions of North Brunswick, Raritan and Franklin Townships. Map is in center, street directory in center bottom and the remaining sides consisting of advertisements from local businesses.
